(SteveWood/www.lostthenfound.info/Handout/Courtesy Madame Tussauds Las Vegas) See the Andy Warhol wax figure in Las Vegas for the first time ever. Madame Tussauds Las Vegas has announced the Warhol wax figure, on loan from Madame Tussauds London, will be on display in Las Vegas from April 24 to Aug. 1, 2014 at Polaroid Fotobar ’s new flagship retail shop, along with an exhibition of Warhol’s artwork and artifacts presented by The Andy Warhol Museum. Admission to The Polaroid Museum on April 24 is free from 10 a.m. to 5 p.m.
